spec: agent-core.ai-docs/v1
namespace: "Domain\\Command"
fqcn: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Command"
updatedAt: 2026-04-19
description: "Command value objects for the agent loop — kind constants, pending queue items, and routed commands with core/extension/rejected discrimination."
files[3]{file,type,summary}:
  PendingCommand.php,readonly final class,"Represents a pending command within the agent core domain, encapsulating execution metadata and input data. This immutable value object ensures type safety and consistency for command processing workflows."
  CoreCommandKind.php,final class,Defines a constant set of core command types within the agent domain. It provides a centralized registry for identifying commands that belong to the core system functionality. This class acts as a discriminator for command routing and validation.
  RoutedCommand.php,readonly final class,"RoutedCommand is a value object representing a domain command with a specific status, kind, and payload. It distinguishes between core and extension commands and supports a rejected state with an optional reason. The class is immutable and provides factory methods for construction."